uk.gov.gchq.palisade.data.service.reader

Class DataFlavour

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.data.service.reader.DataFlavour

  • public class DataFlavour
extends java.lang.Object
    In Palisade, to process a resource, e.g. to de-serialise it, we must know its data type (what type of object the resource contains, e.g. employee records) and its serialised format (how it is stored, e.g. Avro). A DataFlavour is the combination of these two features.
